WEBVTT

00:00:00.571 --> 00:00:03.358
Podignite ruke, ako su vas ikada pitali:

00:00:03.382 --> 00:00:06.382
"Šta želite da budete kad porastete?"

00:00:06.697 --> 00:00:08.362
Sad, kad biste morali da nagađate,

00:00:08.362 --> 00:00:11.557
šta mislite koliko ste imali godina
kada su vas prvi put to pitali?

00:00:11.557 --> 00:00:13.386
Možete samo da podignete prste.

00:00:13.999 --> 00:00:18.632
Tri. Pet. Tri. Pet. Pet. U redu.

00:00:19.376 --> 00:00:23.332
Sad, podignite ruku, ako vam je pitanje:

00:00:23.356 --> 00:00:25.378
"Šta želite da budete kad porastete?"

00:00:25.402 --> 00:00:27.932
ikada uzrokovalo nespokoj.

00:00:27.956 --> 00:00:29.586
(Smeh)

00:00:29.610 --> 00:00:31.832
Bar blagi nespokoj.